Subject: User cannot access USB
Description: Hi there, one of our users cannot access USB on his computer. He is in the right security group and everything looks fine from our AD side and his permission within Endpoint Protector. Do you know what could be going wrong or where I can look?
What_We_Know__c:
The customer updated the EPP Server during the night.
Today I had to optimize the resources on the EPP Server as the server returned a lot of 500 internal errors when accessing pages
Next_Steps__c: The customers will check if EasyLock works as expected today and they will get back to us with an update.
Solution_Comment__c: AD sync issue + resolved afterwards. Closing ticket. No further feedback from the customer.
